What does this MATLAB code display?

```
x = [1 2 3 4 5];
s = sum(x);
n = length(x);
disp(s / n)
```

What does this MATLAB loop display?

```
x = [1 2 3 4 5];
s = 0;
for k = 1:length(x)
    s = s + x(k);
end
disp(s)
```

Trace this MATLAB loop that accumulates a sum of squares.

```
x = [1 2 3 4];
ss = 0;
for k = 1:length(x)
    ss = ss + x(k)^2;
end
disp(ss)
```
